            <p style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#505050; clear:both; display:block; padding:0; margin:0; line-height:normal; text-align:justify;">A versatile removable clear label material useful for commercial, industrial and retail applications. Particularly useful on product packaging where a very high level of flexibility or squeezability is required (e.g. soap and shower gel containers). A good choice for primary brand and product labels on rigid containers where it is important for the content to be visible and not partially obscured by a label. Also secondary promotional labels, informational labels, external labels/signage and safety labels/signage, designed to be removed post purchase. The label face-stock material is suitable for Thermal Transfer printing with specific ribbons. </p></td>
